<p>
A statement that updates the value of a variable.
The format of an assignment statement is as follows:
</p>
<ol>
<li>the name of a <a href="glossary.php?term=variable">variable</a>, followed by</li>
<li>an equals sign, followed by</li>
<li>an <a href="glossary.php?term=expression">expression</a>.</li>
</ol>
<p>
The statement is executed by evaluating the expression on the right 
of the equals sign, and assigning the resulting value to the variable
on the left.
</p>
